	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Adding A Portlet</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Add button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">
			Fill up the following fields, as describe below:<br>
			<li>Name - Portlet name</li>
			<li>Title - Portlet title as appear on the dashboard</li>
			<li>Class/Context - JSP class file</li>
			<li>Description - Description of the portlet</li>
			<li>Themes - Select themes to associate with the portlet. The portlet will be available in the theme.</li>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Add button to save new portlet.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Editing A Portlet</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Portlet name.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Changes can be made to all fields.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Add preferences if have any.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Update button to save the changes made.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Deleting A Portlet</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To delete any existing portlet registry, put a tick in checkbox at portlets that wish to be deleted.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Delete button, a confirmation pop-up message will appear before portlet is deleted. Click on the OK button to delete or Cancel button to cancel.</td>
